2.DevOps Engineerâ€™s Role in SDLC ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’»ğŸ”„

As a DevOps engineer, your main goal is to automate and streamline the processes involved in building, testing, and deploying software. Letâ€™s delve into these phases in detail:

1. Building Phase (Developing) ğŸ› ï¸

- Continuous Integration (CI): Automating the process of integrating code changes from multiple developers into a shared repository several times a day. ğŸ”„
- Tools: Jenkins, GitLab CI, CircleCI. ğŸ› ï¸
