3.How DevOps Improves Efficiency âš¡ï¸

- Automation: Reduces manual intervention, thereby minimizing human errors and increasing speed. ğŸ¤–
- Scalability: Ensures that systems can handle increased loads by automating scaling processes. ğŸ“ˆ
